ID = eClass_BAB299006
Name = Product utilization
Description = N/A
eCl@ss Description = intended use in the sense of this norm is the use for which the technical product is suitable according to the information provided by the manufacturer, including the information used for advertising. If in doubt, this is the use that is typical for the construction type, design and function of the technical product. the intended use also includes the adherence to the prescribed operating and maintenance conditions as well as consideration of the anticipated error behavior
